  "description": "A stunning sunset over a body of water, likely a bay or estuary, features a silhouetted suspension bridge spanning the distance. The sun, just out of frame, casts a brilliant golden reflection across the water, creating a shimmering path towards the bridge. A large ship is visible in the middle ground, also silhouetted against the light. The foreground shows dark shapes of trees and vegetation. The sky is filled with dramatic, dark clouds tinged with orange and gold from the setting sun. The overall composition is one of serene beauty and vastness.",
